<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَدَقَّ بِرِجْلِهِ الأَرْضَ احْتِجَاجَاً<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمَدَّ ذِرَاعَهُ سَهْمَاً يُشِيرُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَبَالَغَ في الْبُكَاءِ بِغَيْرِ دَمْعٍ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لِيُرْغِمَ أَهْلَهُ الطَّاغِي الصَّغِيرُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَصَاحَ أُرِيدُ مِن هَذَا فَهَاتُواْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَإِلاَّ لَن أَسِيرَ وَلَنْ تَسِيرُواْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَوَالِدُهُ يَقُولُ لَهُ أَطِعْني<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>رُكُوبُ الرَّأْسِ شَرٌّ مُسْتَطِيرُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>تَعَقَّلْ يَا بُنيَّ وَسِرْ وَعَيْبٌ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تجَمَّعَ حَوْلَنَا خَلْقٌ كَثِيرُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
